16:27.237 --> 16:29.869
- What's your plan for them?

16:29.869 --> 16:31.571
- We're trying to put together
a music video.

16:31.571 --> 16:34.204
We just have to find
a really great director.

16:34.204 --> 16:37.117
- Totally. This has been
